name: Zynsoft
overview:
This company focus on useful apps for daily life:

  1. Big Photo for iOS - an unique app to handle accurate picture details on iOS devices. Up and close viewing images of ANY sizes. Precise crop and resize to pixel level. http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/big-photo/id513663883?mt=8

  2. Browser 2Go - a very fast web browser for iOS devices. Support tabbed, full screen browsing. We page saver. FTP browser with upload and download. Ad blocker. Translation. JQuery console. Convenient Start Page… http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/browser-2go/id473825218?mt=8

  3. Financial Aid Maximizer for iPad and Mac. Estimate eligible financial aid amount. Provide asset allocation strategies to maximize financial aid amount and tax savings. Jointly developed with Turbo Tuition Inc. http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/financial-aid-maximizer/id532798414?mt=12 http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/fame-financial-aid-maximizer/id525331063?mt=8

  4. FotoMed HD for mobile medical reference, search and photo logging. http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/fotomed-hd/id453824630?mt=8

More interesting apps in cooking…
